{"tid":652841,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"上連登既心理戰","createTime":"2018-05-04T07:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T10:00:55.000Z","uid":22898,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"65e9e9ff1aa24f83eac1529af3ed70aa96b5379d","tid":652841,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T07:22:24.000Z","msg":"先沖出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比人發現之後，一定會有人屌尻你或笑你，唔洗驚，扮假膠，一定要回一句：「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又有真心膠」<br />\n<br />\n之後對方一定又會回你：「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n依粒膠其實只係用黎嚇一嚇你，等你唔知對方究竟有冇識穿你扮假膠，依個時候唔好怕，回返佢一粒：「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n之後！等其他人睇你地既留意，睇下你水到幾多路人信你本身係假膠幫你，接下來就係用正負皮決戰既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係連登柒左扮一扮假膠就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁問題黎啦，如果我真係一開始想做假膠咁點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁依個時候你要反其道而行，說服自己係個真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再跟反上面個做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明唔明？ 其實我都唔係好明"},{"pid":"2a448423f7beda70ae72ad08ea5c00b48ee2012e","tid":652841,"uid":43530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T07:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9582a88fa61b24bc5ebbb44c09a6df16cf37574","tid":652841,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a448423f7beda70ae72ad08ea5c00b48ee2012e","tid":652841,"uid":43530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T07:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 